    <body>
        <div class="header">
        <h1>Ramsey's Secretary</h1>
        <hr>
        <h2>Authorize the Secretary to view your 3rd party connections. </h2>
        <h2>For the Secretary to function properly, you must have your xbox account linked to your Discord.</h2>
        </div>

        <span class="warning">An error has occored. See below for common fixes.</span>

        <div class="permsAlign" style="background-color:rgb(69, 66, 73)">
            <span class="permsHeader" style="color:rgb(135, 236, 140); font-family: Windlass;">Queue Position</span>
            <span class="permsHeader" style="color:rgb(159, 184, 199); font-family: Helvetica;">1/1</span>
            <span class="permsHeader" style="color:rgb(159, 184, 199); font-family: Helvetica;">0:00</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bugList">
            <div class="bug">Verify Xbox account is linked to Discord
                <div class="bugDesc"><span class="bugContentHeader">This is the most common issue and can easily be fixed.</span>
                    <div class="bugContent">
                    <li>Go to your Discord Settings > Connections</li>
                    <li>At the top you should see the following</li>
                    <img src="connections.png"/>
                    <li>Click on the xbox icon and follow the provided steps.</li>
                    <li>Once linked go back and retry!</li>
                </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bug">Authorize the secretary
                <div class="bugDesc"><span class="bugContentHeader">The secretary mush be authorized to view your connections and identity.</span>
                    <div class="bugContent">
                    <li>Be sure to click Authorize when you see this page durring the setup process</li>
                    <img src="auth.png" width=50% height=50%/>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <span class="contact">If none of the above fixes work contact me on Discord at <a href="discord.gg/XruZ6aYhmS">Aurorelyn#4695</a></span>
        </div>

